Here's the PlantUML sequence diagram for the deployment process of the mebaysan_Modern-Data-Architecture system:

```plantuml
@startuml mebaysan_Modern-Data-Architecture
actor User
participant "Docker Compose" as DockerCompose
participant "Airbyte" as Airbyte
participant "PostgreSQL" as Postgres
participant "DBT" as DBT
participant "Apache Superset" as Superset
participant "Nginx" as Nginx

User -> DockerCompose: docker-compose up
DockerCompose -> Airbyte: Start container
DockerCompose -> Postgres: Start container
DockerCompose -> Superset: Start container
DockerCompose -> Nginx: Start container (optional)

Airbyte -> Postgres: Connect to database
Superset -> Postgres: Connect to database
DBT -> Postgres: Connect to database

alt Using Airbyte
    User -> Airbyte: Configure data source (CSV)
    Airbyte -> Postgres: Extract and load raw data
else Using Python Script
    User -> Postgres: Execute script.py
    Postgres -> Postgres: Load CSV data
end

User -> DBT: Run transformations
DBT -> Postgres: Transform data models

User -> Superset: Configure data source
Superset -> Postgres: Query transformed data
Superset -> User: Display visualizations

opt Nginx Proxy
    User -> Nginx: Access pgAdmin
    Nginx -> Postgres: Proxy requests
end
@enduml
```